Ran quality control
I have implemented the 3D Live Wallpaper feature with a modern, trendy UI/UX design. This unique feature allows users to create immersive parallax wallpapers using AI-powered depth analysis.
Key Features of the 3D Live Wallpaper Tool:
Immersive 3D Parallax Preview: A high-end preview area where images tilt and shift in real-time based on mouse movement, creating a stunning depth effect.
AI Depth Analysis: Integrated with Gemini 3.1 Pro to analyze uploaded images and suggest how to separate foreground, middle ground, and background elements for the best 3D effect.
Trendy Glassmorphism UI: The tool features floating UI elements, backdrop blurs, and vibrant pink-to-purple gradients, following the latest design trends.
Dynamic Controls: Users can adjust the "Depth Intensity" to fine-tune the parallax strength.
Smooth Animations: Powered by framer-motion for fluid transitions and interactive feedback.
You can find this new tool under the Media Tools category on your dashboard. It’s designed to be both a creative utility and a showcase of modern web design capabilities.
